ğŸ“Œ C++ programming mein, user input ko input karne ke liye, aapko "<iostream>" library ke functions ka use karna hoga. Yeh functions hai:

ğŸ“ 1: cin: Yeh function, user se input ko program mein input karne ke liye use hoti hai. Yeh function, user se input ko variable mein store karta hai.

ğŸ¯ğŸ¯ğŸ¯ExampleğŸ¯ğŸ¯ğŸ¯:

#include <iostream>

