ğŸ“Œ C++ programming mein, if-else ke saath, ek condition check karne ke liye, aapko if statement ka use karna hoga. Yeh statement, condition check karne ke liye use hota hai. Agar condition true hai toh, if block chalta hai aur agar condition false hai toh, else block chalta hai.

