ğŸ¯ğŸ¯ğŸ¯ExampleğŸ¯ğŸ¯ğŸ¯:

#include <iostream>

int main() {
    int a = 10;
    int b = 20;

    if (a > b) {
        std::cout << "a is greater than b" << std::endl;
    } else {
        std::cout << "b is greater than a" << std::endl;
    }

    return 0;
}

ğŸ“Œ Is example mein, "a" aur "b" mein se, "b" value greater hai. Isliye, condition false hai aur else block chalta hai aur "b is greater than a" print kiya gaya hai.

